reload.desc: Reloads a module, if it fails while reloading, it will spit an error as a txt file

load.desc: Loads a module, if it fails while loading, it will spit an error as a txt file

unload.desc: Unloads a module, if it fails whileun loading, it will spit an error as a txt file

help.desc: Sends dedicated help for a specific command, if no command is specified, it will send a list of all commands

info.desc:
Sends information about the bot, this includes:
Total Guilds, Total Members, Bot Version, Python Version and Bot Uptime

invite.brief: Sends an invite link for the bot and the bot's support server
invite.desc: Sends an invite link for the bot and the bot's support server

ping.desc: Sends the bots latency, which is the latency between a HEARTBEAT and a HEARTBEAT_ACK in miliseconds
